  Cotton-producing State

 means each of the following States and combination of States:
Alabama; Arizona; Arkansas; California-Nevada; Florida; Georgia;
Kansas; Louisiana; Mississippi; Missouri-Illinois; New Mexico; North
Carolina; Oklahoma; South Carolina; Tennessee-Kentucky; Texas;
Virginia.

